    "description": "进入电动汽车世界，管理自己的电动汽车充电站！<br>在《电动汽车充电站》游戏中，你有机会扮演电动汽车充电站的主人。你的任务多种多样，充满挑战，从基本的客户服务到在车间里进行小型维修。这不是一个普通的充电站--在这里，每天都会有新的挑战，您要负责整个企业的高效运营！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/cbab204c9b17cfffe865ec73da666e20.poster.avif?t=1749113262\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/cbab204c9b17cfffe865ec73da666e20.webm?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/cbab204c9b17cfffe865ec73da666e20.mp4?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>节约并产生自己的能源！您的发电站可以使用可再生能源供电。安装太阳能电池组件，降低车站运营成本，并将多余的能源储存在特殊的储能设施中。当您的业务发展得足够好时，您可以投资更好的其他能源，以提供额外的电力。这些解决方案将使您的电站更加自给自足和环保！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/0588e1b40af9adde155c7115bae2ae52.poster.avif?t=1749113262\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/0588e1b40af9adde155c7115bae2ae52.webm?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/0588e1b40af9adde155c7115bae2ae52.mp4?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>运营一个电站在技术上也很有挑战性。有时充电器会出现故障，光伏电池板需要定期清洁--这些只是您需要解决的部分问题。您对电站的技术状况维护得越好，您的业务功能就越完善。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/58cdb718fef0719c46afd6fa774fbd79.poster.avif?t=1749113262\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/58cdb718fef0719c46afd6fa774fbd79.webm?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/58cdb718fef0719c46afd6fa774fbd79.mp4?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>电站开发是成功的关键。用更高效的新型太阳能电池板取代旧电池板，最大限度地提高能源生产。为充电站增设车间，以进行更先进的车辆维修。投资新技术，增加充电站数量，优化能源成本。每一次投资和发展都是朝着建设一个强大的充电站迈出的一步。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/9ce8093403c28eac78403570b96b5d90.poster.avif?t=1749113262\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/9ce8093403c28eac78403570b96b5d90.webm?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174380/extras/9ce8093403c28eac78403570b96b5d90.mp4?t=1749113262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您准备好成为电动汽车行业的领导者了吗？您的成功取决于您的管理技能、快速决策和对细节的敏锐洞察力。迎接挑战，看看你能否打造出最现代化的充电站！<br>特点<br>- 客户服务、电动汽车充电、电池更换站<br>- 小型车辆维修<br>- 充电站的现代化、扩建和发展<br>- 可再生能源投资和能源消耗管理<br>- 关注充电站基础设施的技术状况<br>- 技术和后勤挑战",
